name: Bounty Token: Lady's Brooch
desc:
A broken gear from the clockwork meka. It can be submitted at "The Flagship" as proof of a bounty fulfilled.
"'Ah, my good sir, I could never forget the day I first laid eyes on that lady's captivating grace. Since that moment, she has never left my thoughts. She's not one to obey the will of others. If you should meet her, tread carefully â€” don't be drawn in by her dazzling beauty, like a moth to a flame.'"
